**제거:**
- `.traffic-light`, `.light`, `.light-*`, `.eval-signal`, `.eval-label`, `status-*` (신호등 관련)
- `.summary-body`, `.summary-sub-title`, `.fold-icon`, `.summary-item`, `.kw-tabs`, `.kw-tab`, `.kw-panel` (폴딩·탭 관련)

